Motivated Seller! Ready for a new owner come see this MOVE IN READY top-level condominium in The Woods of Ortega. This 2-bedroom 2- bath home will not last long. New flooring throughout living and dining rooms and bedrooms. Stainless steel   
appliances with new dishwasher and microwave new Washer/ Dryer included. Patio with storage closet. Low Condo fees.  This condo is close to shopping at the Orange Park Mall and Oakleaf Plantation Town Center, restaurants and NAS JAX Base and highways.
